title: Cyber Fighting Action Game Music Pack
longDescription:
https://soundcloud.com/user-511094824/sets/cyber-fighting-action-game-music-pack

This music pack contains 10 loopable and non loopable unique tracks. Perfect for any fighting or action packed game which requires a techie sounding edge for our cyber industrial age. Just don't call those fighting kids cyber punks.

What more needs to be said, have a listen and then check the links below.
